rows.label: qev086304_MSG0004
rows.name:
This is exactly why we counseled against
coming here and provoking it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_SEL0012
rows.name: Claim you'll be back to finish it off.

rows.label: qev086304_SEL0022
rows.name:
Say that you and the Ruler of Fates
understand each other.

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0008
rows.name: You'd need to train for a lifetime to have even half a chance...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0010
rows.name: Then I won't try to stop you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0011
rows.name:
The legends do claim that the Ruler of Fates
can read the hearts of those it sees, to judge their worth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0012
rows.name:
Perhaps we were just fortunate enough
to be judged worthy in the end?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0015
rows.name: It appears to be a guardian etherscale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0016
rows.name: Really? Yes! Now Tora can make his remedy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0017
rows.name: It seems we passed the test...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086304_MSG0017_2
rows.name:
Always nice to know the neighbors
are okay with you moving in.[ST:wait ]
